data.description:
Motivated Sellers! Taking all offers! Seller will contribute $5,000 towards closing costs. Discover your dream home in the sought-after Port St. John area of Cocoa, Florida. This charming 3-bed, 2-bath residence offers a warm and welcoming atmosphere.
Updated kitchen, featuring modern finishes and granite countertops. The bathrooms have also been tastefully updated.
All three bedrooms come with walk-in closets and vinyl plank flooring, combining ample storage with style with durability.
Step outside to your expansive yard, fully fenced for privacy and security. It's a great space for outdoor activities and even has gate access for your boat or RV. Enjoy the Florida weather on your large screened porch!
New HE AC 2023, Roof 2017, No HOA. Enjoy Easy access to 95 and Orlan
